---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import SectionHeading from '../components/SectionHeading.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About" description="About Your Name: education, interests, skills, and current work.">
  <section class="container page-hero">
    <p class="eyebrow">About</p>
    <h1>关于我</h1>
    <p>这里是一个可持续更新的个人背景页，用来组织学习经历、研究兴趣、技能栈和近期方向。</p>
  </section>

  <div class="container page-grid">
    <aside class="side-note">把这里替换成你的学校、年级、实验室、导师或一句更具体的个人定位。</aside>
    <div>
      <section class="page-section">
        <SectionHeading title="About Me" />
        <p>我是 Your Name，一名理工科学生，关注 AI、机器人、科学计算和软件工具。我喜欢把课程、科研和工程项目整理成可复用的笔记与作品。</p>
      </section>

      <section class="page-section">
        <SectionHeading title="Education" />
        <div class="info-block">
          <h3>Your University</h3>
          <p>B.Eng. / B.Sc. in Your Major, 20XX - 20XX</p>
          <p>Relevant focus: machine learning, control systems, algorithms, numerical methods.</p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="page-section">
        <SectionHeading title="Interests" />
        <ul>
          <li>AI / Machine Learning for scientific and engineering problems</li>
          <li>Robotics, control, embedded sensing, and autonomy</li>
          <li>Scientific computing, simulation, and technical visualization</li>
          <li>Developer tools and web-based learning tools</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="page-section">
        <SectionHeading title="Skills" />
        <div class="grid grid-3">
          <div class="info-block">
            <h3>Programming</h3>
            <p>Python, C/C++, TypeScript, MATLAB, SQL</p>
          </div>
          <div class="info-block">
            <h3>Tools</h3>
            <p>Git, Linux, Docker, Jupyter, LaTeX, Astro</p>
          </div>
          <div class="info-block">
            <h3>Domain Knowledge</h3>
            <p>Machine learning, control, embedded systems, numerical analysis</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="page-section">
        <SectionHeading title="What I’m Working On" />
        <p>目前正在整理课程项目、论文阅读模板和可复现实验流程。之后可以在这里放实验室项目、毕业设计或实习方向。</p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
